=> Authentication Filter
	- If we add Spring security we will be adding Authentication Filter, which will intercept request before controller 
	- Authentication filter grab the username and password and create authentication object 
	- Object is shared to Authentication Manager-> it will delegate authentication task to Authentication Provider-> validates credentials with UserDetails and PasswordEncoder
	
	- UserDetailsService will load user details with Username
	- Once Authentication is done the authenticated object is given back to Authentication Manager then Authentication filter which will store in Security Context
	
